net.brabenetz.lib.securedproperties.config

Class AbstractConfigInitializer

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.brabenetz.lib.securedproperties.config.AbstractConfigInitializer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConfigInitializer
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConfigByEnvProperties, ConfigByPropertyFile, ConfigBySystemProperties

    public abstract class AbstractConfigInitializer
extends Object
implements ConfigInitializer
    Parent helper class to easier implement a custom ConfigInitializer. Only getValue(ConfigKey) must be implemented.
